{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "01", "m": "04", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "07", "M": "06", "S": "27"}}, "news": [{"title": "HYDRAA frees 8.24-acre lake on Hyderabad outskirts of encroachments", "para": "Hyderabad Disaster Response and Asset Protection Agency, HYDRAA, took action across the city on Tuesday. Encroachments on Nagireddy Kunta lake were removed. Roadside structures in Bowrampet were cleared. Land designated for a park in Avushapur was reclaimed. A stormwater drain in Jubilee Hills was restored. These operations followed complaints and field verification.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/hydraa-takes-bold-action-to-clear-encroachments-from-824-acre-lake-in-hyderabad/129939908?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-208390/129939908.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Bhubaneswar development body signs pact with Singapore firm for new city's master plan", "para": "Bhubaneswar Development Authority has partnered with Singapore-based Surbana Jurong to create a master plan for Bhubaneswar New City, an 800-acre urban expansion project. This initiative aims to establish a multi-economic growth zone with transit-oriented development, affordable housing, and smart, green infrastructure to guide the capital's future growth and enhance liveability.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/bhubaneswar-development-authority-partners-with-singapores-surbana-jurong-for-new-city-master-plan/129939876?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-108932/129939876.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Tier-II city homebuyers in Karnataka drive up demand for duplex apartments", "para": "Duplex apartments are gaining popularity in North Karnataka cities like Hubballi and Belagavi. This trend, driven by buyer demand, offers spacious living and privacy. Developers are responding to this shift, with a notable increase in duplex and penthouse constructions. Buyers are opting for these homes for safety, shared maintenance, and customized interiors, redefining urban living in these growing cities.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/growing-demand-for-duplex-apartments-in-karnatakas-tier-ii-cities/129939806?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-26838/129939806.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}]}